00:00:07.033 --> 00:00:10.234 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>But you came all this way</i>
 <i>to visit our hot spring...</i>

00:00:10.267 --> 00:00:13.367 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>You should relax and stay</i>
 <i>a bit longer.</i>

00:00:13.400 --> 00:00:15.801 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Well, since I'm an</i>
 <i>impatient man.</i>

00:00:15.834 --> 00:00:19.400 position:21% line:77% align:start
 <i>There seems to be a</i>
 <i>storm headed our way, so</i>
 <i>be careful.</i>

00:00:20.567 --> 00:00:22.300 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Thank you very much for</i>
 <i>everything.</i>

00:00:30.901 --> 00:00:32.834 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>I'd better hurry.</i>

00:00:38.400 --> 00:00:41.534 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>You're Tadaichi, a shinobi of</i>
 <i>the Hidden Leaf, correct?</i>

00:00:42.667 --> 00:00:46.200 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Well, yes, I am from the</i>
 <i>Hidden Leaf.</i>

00:00:46.234 --> 00:00:50.033 position:38% line:77% align:start
 <i>But I wouldn't call</i>
 <i>myself a shinobi. I'm</i>
 <i>just a lowly merchant.</i>

00:00:50.067 --> 00:00:52.033 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>You can't fool me.</i>

00:00:52.067 --> 00:00:56.067 position:16% line:77% align:start
 <i>I checked up on you and</i>
 <i>found out what you did</i>
 <i>when were in the ANBU.</i>

00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:00.567 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>Visual Jutsu?!</i>

00:01:08.701 --> 00:01:10.234 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>Beautifully done.</i>

00:01:12.534 --> 00:01:15.200 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>"I'm going to dye it all red."</i>

00:02:56.267 --> 00:02:59.834 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>"Sasuke's Story: Sunrise, Part</i>
 <i>1: The Exploding Human."</i>

00:02:59.868 --> 00:03:02.634 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Kakashi) So, what are you doing</i>
 <i>here?</i>

00:03:02.667 --> 00:03:04.868 position:21% line:83% align:start
Sakura said she was
gonna come to see you...

00:03:04.901 --> 00:03:07.534 position:13% line:83% align:start
so I figured that I'd just
tag along with her, you know?

00:03:07.567 --> 00:03:08.868 position:5% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:03:09.868 --> 00:03:12.634 position:24% line:83% align:start
All right, Sakura,
what is it?

00:03:12.667 --> 00:03:18.234 position:5% line:77% align:start
Recently, there've been a number
of incidents in which Hidden
Leaf shinobi have gone missing.

00:03:18.267 --> 00:03:19.501 position:5% line:89% align:start
They've gone missing?

00:03:19.534 --> 00:03:20.434 position:44% line:89% align:start
Mhm.

00:03:21.200 --> 00:03:23.367 position:19% line:83% align:start
So you noticed it too,
huh?

00:03:23.400 --> 00:03:25.934 position:47% line:83% align:start
You already knew,
Kakashi Sensei?

00:03:25.968 --> 00:03:30.467 position:5% line:77% align:start
Yes. But why were you
looking into something
like that, Sakura?

00:03:30.501 --> 00:03:35.100 position:33% line:77% align:start
Well, you see  there's
a regular at the flower
shop Ino's family runs.

00:03:35.133 --> 00:03:36.067 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:03:37.501 --> 00:03:39.133 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Kakashi) It's coming from the</i>
 <i>Aun Gate.</i>

00:03:40.267 --> 00:03:42.300 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'll go and check it
out, ok guys!

00:03:42.334 --> 00:03:43.067 position:80% line:89% align:start
Eh...

00:03:43.100 --> 00:03:45.400 position:13% line:89% align:start
[grunts] Naruto! Wait up!

00:03:45.434 --> 00:03:46.467 position:30% line:89% align:start
Hey! You two!

00:03:49.534 --> 00:03:52.434 position:16% line:89% align:start
[sigh] Well, good luck.

00:03:52.467 --> 00:03:55.834 position:19% line:83% align:start
Run! Go on, get out of
here, fast! Go! Go!

00:03:56.334 --> 00:03:57.901 position:35% line:89% align:start
[screams]

00:03:57.934 --> 00:04:00.167 position:19% line:89% align:start
[zombie-like groaning]

00:04:01.167 --> 00:04:02.200 position:44% line:89% align:start
The Security Unit!

00:04:04.367 --> 00:04:05.267 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:04:09.200 --> 00:04:10.934 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:04:10.968 --> 00:04:11.968 position:69% line:89% align:start
[inhales]

00:04:12.000 --> 00:04:13.834 position:5% line:83% align:start
Why are they fighting
defensively?

00:04:13.868 --> 00:04:15.767 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'm gonna go and help 'em
out!

00:04:15.801 --> 00:04:16.534 position:5% line:89% align:start
Wait!

00:04:16.567 --> 00:04:17.167 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:04:18.267 --> 00:04:21.100 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>(Naruto) Ino? Shikamaru? Choji?</i>

00:04:21.834 --> 00:04:22.901 position:30% line:89% align:start
What happened?

00:04:23.534 --> 00:04:24.934 position:5% line:89% align:start
It can't be!

00:04:25.434 --> 00:04:26.000 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:04:26.801 --> 00:04:27.834 position:30% line:89% align:start
Mr. Tadaichi!

00:04:27.868 --> 00:04:28.901 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>(Sakura) What?</i>

00:04:28.934 --> 00:04:31.367 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>(Ino) That's Mr. Tadaichi!</i>

00:04:31.400 --> 00:04:35.801 position:5% line:77% align:start
Huh? Just hold on a second. Are
you talking about the flower
shop regular?

00:04:36.133 --> 00:04:37.133 position:44% line:89% align:start
Mhm.

00:04:37.167 --> 00:04:39.234 position:19% line:83% align:start
You're completely sure
that's him, Ino?

00:04:39.267 --> 00:04:41.434 position:5% line:89% align:start
Yeah! There's no mistake!

00:04:41.467 --> 00:04:44.767 position:7% line:83% align:start
But still, he would never turn
against the Hidden Leaf!

00:04:46.000 --> 00:04:47.868 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>(Ino) So why?</i>

00:04:47.901 --> 00:04:48.601 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:04:50.067 --> 00:04:54.167 position:5% line:77% align:start
Then does that mean he
could've been put under a
genjutsu? It makes sense.

00:04:54.200 --> 00:04:57.868 position:5% line:77% align:start
Uh! And the others could be the
people that have gone
missing!

00:04:57.901 --> 00:04:59.200 position:5% line:89% align:start
What!? No way!

00:04:59.234 --> 00:05:03.300 position:38% line:83% align:start
You mean, those guys
are Hidden Leaf shinobi?

00:05:03.334 --> 00:05:06.934 position:5% line:83% align:start
[grunts] So that's why Security
was on the defensive.

00:05:06.968 --> 00:05:13.067 position:21% line:89% align:start
[zombie-like groans]

00:05:13.434 --> 00:05:14.567 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:05:14.601 --> 00:05:15.501 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:05:17.634 --> 00:05:19.000 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:05:20.968 --> 00:05:22.968 position:21% line:83% align:start
He didn't even dodge
it.

00:05:23.000 --> 00:05:24.033 position:5% line:89% align:start
[worried reaction]

00:05:27.567 --> 00:05:28.901 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:05:28.934 --> 00:05:30.701 position:5% line:89% align:start
Doesn't he feel any pain?

00:05:41.868 --> 00:05:44.701 position:38% line:89% align:start
[coughs]

00:05:46.300 --> 00:05:47.934 position:24% line:89% align:start
[gasps] What the?!

00:05:48.534 --> 00:05:50.501 position:21% line:89% align:start
Shadow Clone Jutsu!

00:05:51.901 --> 00:05:52.501 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:05:53.834 --> 00:05:54.968 position:38% line:89% align:start
Naruto?

00:05:55.000 --> 00:05:56.667 position:5% line:89% align:start
Quick! Jump!

00:06:16.734 --> 00:06:19.534 position:13% line:83% align:start
No way! That guy was like
a human bomb!

00:06:20.033 --> 00:06:21.467 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>(Ino) Tadaichi.</i>

00:06:25.200 --> 00:06:26.467 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm okay.

00:06:27.968 --> 00:06:29.567 position:24% line:83% align:start
Let's tend to the
wounded.

00:06:32.834 --> 00:06:34.501 position:21% line:89% align:start
[zombie-like groans]

00:06:34.534 --> 00:06:35.367 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>(Shikamaru) Hey!</i>

00:06:35.400 --> 00:06:37.200 position:5% line:83% align:start
They're getting
into the Village!

00:06:37.234 --> 00:06:39.067 position:33% line:89% align:start
Oh, no! Not them, too!

00:06:39.100 --> 00:06:44.434 position:21% line:89% align:start
[zombie-like groans]

00:06:44.701 --> 00:06:45.934 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:06:51.834 --> 00:06:53.567 position:24% line:89% align:start
That thing's really huge!

00:06:53.601 --> 00:06:54.300 position:5% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:06:55.267 --> 00:06:57.601 position:5% line:83% align:start
Choji, can you make
wings with your expansion?

00:06:57.634 --> 00:06:59.167 position:58% line:89% align:start
Sure, got it!

00:07:00.834 --> 00:07:05.334 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chewing]

00:07:05.367 --> 00:07:06.868 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:07:07.767 --> 00:07:11.601 position:38% line:89% align:start
[yells]

00:07:13.567 --> 00:07:14.968 position:38% line:89% align:start
[yells]

00:07:17.734 --> 00:07:21.434 position:19% line:83% align:start
All right! We'll help
too! Let's go Kurama!

00:07:21.467 --> 00:07:22.467 position:5% line:89% align:start
Right!

00:07:25.133 --> 00:07:26.567 position:27% line:89% align:start
[attacking yell]

00:07:32.334 --> 00:07:34.534 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groans]

00:07:34.567 --> 00:07:36.567 position:5% line:89% align:start
[grunts] Did that do the trick?

00:07:36.601 --> 00:07:38.267 position:5% line:89% align:start
Yeah, you did great!

00:07:38.300 --> 00:07:41.067 position:24% line:83% align:start
It looks  like this isn't
over just yet, though.

00:07:41.100 --> 00:07:41.767 position:5% line:89% align:start
Hmm?

00:07:44.734 --> 00:07:46.300 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Shikamaru) There's more of</i>
 <i>them?!</i>

00:07:46.334 --> 00:07:47.367 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:07:47.834 --> 00:07:49.868 position:50% line:89% align:start
[grunts] Naruto!

00:07:49.901 --> 00:07:53.300 position:5% line:77% align:start
I'm pretty sure that getting
wounded triggers them to
explode.

00:07:53.334 --> 00:07:58.634 position:5% line:77% align:start
I saw strange chakra being
released from the wound, and
then his body transformed.

00:07:58.667 --> 00:08:02.000 position:5% line:77% align:start
Which means we'll have to
be careful about how we
engage them.

00:08:02.367 --> 00:08:03.367 position:5% line:89% align:start
Naruto!

00:08:03.767 --> 00:08:04.834 position:38% line:89% align:start
Hinata!

00:08:05.767 --> 00:08:07.534 position:19% line:89% align:start
What is going on here?

00:08:07.567 --> 00:08:11.601 position:21% line:83% align:start
Well, it seems like
everyone is under a genjutsu.

00:08:11.634 --> 00:08:14.434 position:16% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Naruto) Can you see if</i>
 <i>someone's controlling them</i>
 <i>somewhere?</i>

00:08:14.467 --> 00:08:16.901 position:5% line:83% align:start
Okay I'll take a
look.

00:08:17.834 --> 00:08:19.133 position:35% line:89% align:start
Byakugan!

00:08:23.767 --> 00:08:25.434 position:21% line:89% align:start
I don't see anyone.

00:08:25.467 --> 00:08:26.567 position:21% line:89% align:start
[frustrated grunts]

00:08:26.601 --> 00:08:27.567 position:52% line:89% align:start
There's no one?

00:08:27.601 --> 00:08:29.200 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mh-m.

00:08:29.234 --> 00:08:31.601 position:27% line:83% align:start
Then how are all of them
being manipulated?

00:08:33.334 --> 00:08:37.367 position:13% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Hinata) There's a foreign</i>
 <i>chakra running through every</i>
 <i>inch of their bodies.</i>

00:08:37.400 --> 00:08:40.467 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>It's possible that it's what's</i>
 <i>controlling them.</i>

00:08:40.501 --> 00:08:43.234 position:5% line:77% align:start
So we just have to
remove that chakra
then?

00:08:43.267 --> 00:08:44.834 position:80% line:89% align:start
Mh-m.

00:08:44.868 --> 00:08:49.133 position:16% line:83% align:start
The chakra. It's circulating
like it's part of their bodies.

00:08:49.167 --> 00:08:51.701 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Hinata) It might be fused to</i>
 <i>them internally.</i>

00:08:51.734 --> 00:08:55.968 position:5% line:77% align:start
So you're saying that we can't
simply tear it out of all
of them, huh?

00:08:56.000 --> 00:08:59.968 position:5% line:77% align:start
Well all right, first
things first. We have to
start by capturing them.

00:09:00.000 --> 00:09:04.901 position:10% line:77% align:start
But Shikamaru it's going to be
tough to capture so many without
hurting them.

00:09:04.934 --> 00:09:09.300 position:21% line:77% align:start
[gasps] Hey guys! I
just got a great idea!
[chuckles]

00:09:09.868 --> 00:09:13.100 position:21% line:89% align:start
[zombie-like growl]

00:09:13.133 --> 00:09:16.033 position:21% line:89% align:start
[zombie-like groans]

00:09:16.067 --> 00:09:18.367 position:21% line:83% align:start
Okay come on! Let's
go!

00:09:22.567 --> 00:09:26.234 position:10% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Naruto) First, I'll have my</i>
 <i>clones slow down the</i>
 <i>exploding humans.</i>

00:09:27.367 --> 00:09:29.033 position:16% line:89% align:start
Shadow Possession Jutsu!

00:09:30.968 --> 00:09:35.033 position:10% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Naruto) Then Shikamaru will</i>
 <i>capture them with his Shadow</i>
 <i>Possession Jutsu.</i>

00:09:35.067 --> 00:09:36.234 position:21% line:89% align:start
[zombie-like groans]

00:09:36.267 --> 00:09:37.334 position:33% line:89% align:start
Go, Hinata!

00:09:37.367 --> 00:09:38.501 position:41% line:89% align:start
Right!

00:09:38.801 --> 00:09:39.868 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:09:41.801 --> 00:09:45.267 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Naruto) And lastly, Hinata will</i>
 <i>pierce their critical chakra</i>
 <i>points so they can't move.</i>

00:09:45.300 --> 00:09:47.367 position:10% line:83% align:start
They'll be immobilized for a
day.

00:09:48.000 --> 00:09:49.133 position:38% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:09:49.167 --> 00:09:50.667 position:5% line:83% align:start
Hey are you okay
Hinata?

00:09:51.734 --> 00:09:53.100 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yes.

00:09:53.133 --> 00:09:54.634 position:19% line:89% align:start
We'll fight together!

00:09:55.000 --> 00:09:55.667 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:09:57.133 --> 00:09:58.067 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:10:17.467 --> 00:10:19.367 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>(Sakura) It won't work.</i>

00:10:19.400 --> 00:10:25.267 position:10% line:77% align:start
I tried my Counter-Genjutsu
but there's no effect on the
strange chakra in them.

00:10:25.300 --> 00:10:26.534 position:33% line:89% align:start
None at all.

00:10:26.567 --> 00:10:29.968 position:5% line:83% align:start
Hey, don't get so down
on yourself.

00:10:30.000 --> 00:10:35.100 position:5% line:77% align:start
Whoever's behind all this,
they used a genjutsu we've never
seen before.

00:10:35.133 --> 00:10:39.634 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Kakashi) It has to be the work</i>
 <i>of someone with extraordinary</i>
 <i>skill.</i>

00:10:39.667 --> 00:10:44.400 position:16% line:77% align:start
So it'll require someone
with extraordinary Visual
Jutsu.

00:10:44.434 --> 00:10:45.367 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm?

00:10:45.400 --> 00:10:46.801 position:58% line:89% align:start
Visual Jutsu?

00:10:46.834 --> 00:10:47.767 position:75% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:10:47.801 --> 00:10:48.801 position:5% line:89% align:start
[chuckles]

00:10:48.834 --> 00:10:50.701 position:5% line:89% align:start
Yep! Correct!

00:10:50.734 --> 00:10:51.501 position:44% line:89% align:start
Uhh.

00:10:52.467 --> 00:10:54.634 position:19% line:83% align:start
Hold on! I didn't even
say anything at all!

00:10:54.667 --> 00:10:56.634 position:5% line:83% align:start
What do you mean? What
didn't you say?

00:10:56.667 --> 00:10:58.534 position:35% line:89% align:start
Don't ask!

00:10:59.801 --> 00:11:01.267 position:5% line:89% align:start
Naruto!

00:11:01.300 --> 00:11:03.801 position:24% line:83% align:start
We may not be able to see
anything...

00:11:03.834 --> 00:11:08.133 position:10% line:77% align:start
But someone who possesses both
the Sharingan and Rinnegan might
be able to.

00:11:08.167 --> 00:11:09.000 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:11:09.033 --> 00:11:10.400 position:35% line:89% align:start
You mean?

00:11:10.434 --> 00:11:13.501 position:19% line:83% align:start
Yes. I'm going to send
for Sasuke.

00:11:13.534 --> 00:11:14.334 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:11:15.400 --> 00:11:16.400 position:27% line:89% align:start
Could you do it?

00:11:16.734 --> 00:11:17.734 position:41% line:89% align:start
Sure.

00:11:19.934 --> 00:11:21.834 position:16% line:83% align:start
Sasuke's gonna come back
home!

00:11:25.133 --> 00:11:26.234 position:30% line:89% align:start
[pleased sigh]

00:11:38.734 --> 00:11:42.834 position:19% line:83% align:start
Which means that  I am
alone.

00:11:42.868 --> 00:11:47.434 position:21% line:77% align:start
I alone can bear the
weight of all the
hatred in the world now.

00:11:47.467 --> 00:11:50.934 position:24% line:77% align:start
You really don't have any
clue at all about how
Itachi lived!

00:11:52.267 --> 00:11:58.267 position:5% line:83% align:start
Why do you keep on...involving
yourself with me?

00:11:59.334 --> 00:12:01.133 position:33% line:89% align:start
'Cuz you're my friend.

00:12:01.167 --> 00:12:07.601 position:5% line:77% align:start
You've told me that before.
But what exactly does that
mean to you?

00:12:07.634 --> 00:12:12.067 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Naruto) You ask me to explain,</i>
 <i>but it's not like I</i>
 <i>understand it either.</i>

00:12:12.100 --> 00:12:19.133 position:21% line:77% align:start
It's just, when I see you
take on stuff, and get all
messed up, it...

00:12:20.801 --> 00:12:22.534 position:72% line:89% align:start
Kinda...

00:12:23.334 --> 00:12:25.267 position:52% line:89% align:start
Well, hurts me.

00:12:29.167 --> 00:12:30.434 position:38% line:89% align:start
[meows]

00:12:45.601 --> 00:12:46.567 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckles]

00:12:47.501 --> 00:12:48.334 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm?

00:12:50.200 --> 00:12:51.334 position:38% line:89% align:start
[meows]

00:13:19.868 --> 00:13:22.467 position:21% line:83% align:start
Return to the Hidden
Leaf, huh?

00:13:29.501 --> 00:13:33.300 position:19% line:89% align:start
[gasping] He exploded!

00:13:33.334 --> 00:13:35.234 position:24% line:89% align:start
That guy exploded!

00:13:35.267 --> 00:13:36.634 position:21% line:89% align:start
[zombie-like groan]

00:13:37.133 --> 00:13:39.100 position:24% line:89% align:start
[grunts] Damn you!

00:13:39.133 --> 00:13:40.033 position:35% line:89% align:start
No, stop!

00:13:41.868 --> 00:13:43.100 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:13:45.334 --> 00:13:46.267 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:13:46.968 --> 00:13:48.734 position:21% line:89% align:start
[zombie-like groan]

00:13:50.133 --> 00:13:51.267 position:35% line:89% align:start
[frightened reaction]

00:13:52.567 --> 00:13:55.634 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:13:56.601 --> 00:13:57.901 position:38% line:89% align:start
[coughs]

00:13:59.667 --> 00:14:00.701 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:14:00.734 --> 00:14:01.501 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:14:08.133 --> 00:14:13.067 position:19% line:77% align:start
Don't tell me...that's
like the exploding human
that attacked the Leaf.

00:14:13.100 --> 00:14:15.400 position:13% line:89% align:start
Why? A village like this?

00:14:15.434 --> 00:14:16.801 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>(Chino) Old Man Iou!</i>

00:14:17.501 --> 00:14:19.501 position:5% line:89% align:start
[frightened panting]

00:14:19.534 --> 00:14:21.901 position:21% line:89% align:start
[zombie-like groans]

00:14:21.934 --> 00:14:23.934 position:35% line:89% align:start
Chino, go stall them.

00:14:23.968 --> 00:14:25.667 position:21% line:89% align:start
You got it, Nowaki!

00:14:26.901 --> 00:14:29.901 position:16% line:83% align:start
Here goes! Water Style:
Water Wall!

00:14:32.000 --> 00:14:34.467 position:21% line:89% align:start
[zombie-like groans]

00:14:35.200 --> 00:14:36.734 position:38% line:89% align:start
Shinobi?

00:14:39.434 --> 00:14:42.367 position:16% line:83% align:start
What is all this? What's
happening here?

00:14:42.400 --> 00:14:46.968 position:38% line:77% align:start
What?! Who are you?!
Wait a minute! Are you
one of them, too?

00:14:47.000 --> 00:14:48.334 position:21% line:89% align:start
You've got it wrong.

00:14:50.133 --> 00:14:53.868 position:7% line:77% align:start
Just shut up! They ordered you
to come here and get even with
me, didn't they? I know it!

00:14:53.901 --> 00:14:55.901 position:35% line:89% align:start
Get even?

00:14:55.934 --> 00:14:58.901 position:27% line:83% align:start
Hey! Young ones!
What're you waiting for?!

00:14:58.934 --> 00:15:01.000 position:5% line:89% align:start
Oh, come on.

00:15:01.033 --> 00:15:04.167 position:5% line:83% align:start
Sorry. I've got nothing against
you, but...

00:15:06.801 --> 00:15:08.400 position:33% line:89% align:start
Water Style!

00:15:09.968 --> 00:15:11.367 position:35% line:89% align:start
Rain Hail!

00:15:12.367 --> 00:15:14.634 position:21% line:83% align:start
Fire Style: Fireball
Jutsu!

00:15:17.334 --> 00:15:22.100 position:7% line:77% align:start
What? I didn't know that Fire
Style could beat Water Style!
Did you, Nowaki?

00:15:22.133 --> 00:15:23.667 position:30% line:89% align:start
Just get back.

00:15:31.267 --> 00:15:33.534 position:16% line:83% align:start
Change in Chakra Nature
of Wind?

00:15:33.567 --> 00:15:37.868 position:7% line:83% align:start
[grunts] Come on! Hurry up and
kill him!

00:15:37.901 --> 00:15:42.334 position:13% line:77% align:start
[groans] No one ever said
anything about him being so
strong!

00:15:42.367 --> 00:15:45.434 position:47% line:83% align:start
[grunts] Why, you
spineless little brat!

00:15:45.467 --> 00:15:45.868 position:5% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:15:46.934 --> 00:15:49.200 position:21% line:89% align:start
[zombie-like groans]

00:15:49.234 --> 00:15:51.033 position:33% line:89% align:start
Hmm? [gasps]

00:15:53.033 --> 00:15:57.601 position:16% line:77% align:start
After all this, you can
explain why you thought
I was someone else.

00:16:00.901 --> 00:16:02.167 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:16:06.100 --> 00:16:07.534 position:35% line:89% align:start
That eye.

00:16:08.234 --> 00:16:10.100 position:30% line:89% align:start
The Sharingan?

00:16:11.434 --> 00:16:12.934 position:27% line:89% align:start
He's an Uchiha.

00:16:14.400 --> 00:16:17.234 position:13% line:83% align:start
How did the villagers end
up in this condition?

00:16:17.267 --> 00:16:19.234 position:5% line:89% align:start
How should I know that?!

00:16:19.267 --> 00:16:22.868 position:19% line:77% align:start
The one you mistook me
for is involved somehow,
right?

00:16:22.901 --> 00:16:25.234 position:5% line:89% align:start
[grunts] I'm not telling you!

00:16:27.834 --> 00:16:32.234 position:21% line:77% align:start
I-I'm sorry. But we
don't really know what's
going on here either.

00:16:32.267 --> 00:16:33.033 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:16:34.434 --> 00:16:38.434 position:21% line:77% align:start
Seems to me that you
two aren't even from this
village, are you?

00:16:38.467 --> 00:16:42.400 position:52% line:77% align:start
Uh huh. We were
shinobi, but now we're
traveling performers.

00:16:42.434 --> 00:16:47.200 position:7% line:77% align:start
We had a gig at a resort in the
Hot Springs Village. We made
real coin there!

00:16:47.234 --> 00:16:50.567 position:16% line:77% align:start
There's good money to be
found here for
entertainers like us!

00:16:50.601 --> 00:16:52.334 position:35% line:89% align:start
[exhales]

00:16:54.200 --> 00:16:56.901 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Chino) Anyway, after that gig</i>
 <i>ended, we decided to head</i>
 <i>somewhere else...</i>

00:16:56.934 --> 00:17:00.834 position:19% line:77% align:start
 <i>so we came through the</i>
 <i>Bamboo Village to stock up on</i>
 <i>supplies.</i>

00:17:00.868 --> 00:17:05.467 position:21% line:77% align:start
Oh yeah, and Old Man Iou's
daughter is so nice to us! She's
really great!

00:17:05.501 --> 00:17:05.934 position:5% line:89% align:start
Hmph!

00:17:06.801 --> 00:17:08.567 position:50% line:83% align:start
She made us this
amazingly tasty food!

00:17:08.601 --> 00:17:12.534 position:7% line:83% align:start
[grunts] Hey, wait! Amino! Is
she okay?

00:17:13.067 --> 00:17:16.100 position:27% line:89% align:start
Amino! [grunts]

00:17:16.133 --> 00:17:19.701 position:21% line:77% align:start
Earlier, we told all
the women and children to
take shelter.

00:17:24.267 --> 00:17:25.701 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hey!

00:17:29.334 --> 00:17:33.267 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Sasuke) I have no choice but to</i>
 <i>ask these guys directly,</i>
 <i>then.</i>

00:17:33.300 --> 00:17:38.200 position:21% line:83% align:start
[frightened fleeing
efforts]

00:17:41.200 --> 00:17:42.567 position:21% line:83% align:start
[frightened fleeing
efforts]

00:17:42.601 --> 00:17:44.133 position:27% line:89% align:start
[gasps] Amino?!

00:17:44.868 --> 00:17:46.167 position:21% line:89% align:start
An exploding human?!

00:17:47.634 --> 00:17:50.667 position:5% line:83% align:start
Mr. Iou, stay back!
It's too dangerous.

00:17:50.701 --> 00:17:55.601 position:27% line:77% align:start
What?! Who cares if it's
dangerous or not?! Don't you
understand, you fool?

00:17:55.634 --> 00:17:57.033 position:41% line:89% align:start
That's my daughter!

00:17:57.067 --> 00:17:59.701 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>(Iou) Let go! Let me go!</i>

00:18:00.868 --> 00:18:02.234 position:41% line:89% align:start
Amino!

00:18:02.634 --> 00:18:04.033 position:44% line:89% align:start
No!

00:18:09.634 --> 00:18:10.434 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:18:25.334 --> 00:18:27.334 position:27% line:89% align:start
I will never...

00:18:28.267 --> 00:18:31.100 position:38% line:89% align:start
forgive you Fuushin!

00:18:32.000 --> 00:18:35.567 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'll never forgive you,
Fuushin!

00:18:51.167 --> 00:18:52.501 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm?

00:18:52.534 --> 00:18:55.200 position:10% line:89% align:start
Just who is this "Fuushin?"

00:18:55.234 --> 00:18:58.534 position:5% line:89% align:start
The Lightning Gang's leader.

00:18:59.067 --> 00:19:00.300 position:27% line:89% align:start
Lightning Gang?

00:19:03.968 --> 00:19:08.834 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Villager) They take money from</i>
 <i>bad people and distribute it to</i>
 <i>poor people like us.</i>

00:19:08.868 --> 00:19:12.467 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>They're thieves, but</i>
 <i>they act honorably.</i>

00:19:14.000 --> 00:19:17.200 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Sasuke) So why would their</i>
 <i>leader want to get even?</i>

00:19:17.534 --> 00:19:19.100 position:75% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:19:19.133 --> 00:19:22.167 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Villager) This is just what I</i>
 <i>heard.</i>

00:19:22.200 --> 00:19:26.133 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Villager) The Lightning Gang</i>
 <i>was betrayed by the Hidden Mist.</i>

00:19:26.167 --> 00:19:32.300 position:10% line:77% align:start
 <i>It seems they barely escaped</i>
 <i>with their lives and found their</i>
 <i>way to this village.</i>

00:19:34.467 --> 00:19:37.234 position:21% line:77% align:start
Will you let us rest
here, just for a
while?

00:19:37.267 --> 00:19:39.334 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>(Iou) Please go elsewhere.</i>

00:19:39.367 --> 00:19:40.400 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:19:41.767 --> 00:19:45.400 position:5% line:77% align:start
If we give you safe harbor,
we'll end up paying for it very
dearly!

00:19:45.434 --> 00:19:50.467 position:5% line:77% align:start
Please, we have no intention of
troubling the village! We won't
stay long!

00:19:50.501 --> 00:19:53.868 position:7% line:77% align:start
Just cause you take money from
others and give it to those in
need...

00:19:53.901 --> 00:19:56.534 position:19% line:77% align:start
don't think you can do
whatever you want! You
hear?!

00:19:56.567 --> 00:19:57.667 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:19:59.000 --> 00:20:02.033 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Villager) The village turned</i>
 <i>the Lightning Gang away.</i>

00:20:06.667 --> 00:20:08.901 position:33% line:89% align:start
What are you gonna do?

00:20:08.934 --> 00:20:11.567 position:5% line:83% align:start
Search the memories of
the exploding humans.

00:20:11.601 --> 00:20:12.834 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>(Chino) Huh?!</i>

00:20:14.968 --> 00:20:15.868 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:20:49.868 --> 00:20:52.868 position:21% line:89% align:start
[gasping for breath]

00:20:53.834 --> 00:20:55.801 position:33% line:89% align:start
Huh. [gasps]

00:21:03.067 --> 00:21:04.234 position:24% line:89% align:start
[heavy breathing]

00:21:04.934 --> 00:21:07.267 position:35% line:89% align:start
[screams]

00:21:07.667 --> 00:21:09.334 position:72% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:21:10.534 --> 00:21:12.901 position:30% line:89% align:start
Are you okay?

00:21:12.934 --> 00:21:17.801 position:7% line:83% align:start
[exhales] Those crimson eyes,
I'm sure of it!

00:21:19.133 --> 00:21:21.133 position:19% line:89% align:start
It's a Kekkei Genkai.

00:22:53.167 --> 00:22:57.934 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Yamato) You're Sasuke, right?</i>
 <i>You can call me Yamato.</i>

00:22:57.968 --> 00:23:01.100 position:16% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Sasuke) It's about the</i>
 <i>Exploding Humans' attack on the</i>
 <i>Leaf.</i>

00:23:01.133 --> 00:23:05.367 position:10% line:77% align:start
 <i>It's possible Orochimaru may</i>
 <i>have information about the</i>
 <i>person behind it.</i>

00:23:05.400 --> 00:23:08.434 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>(Yamato) It'd be easier for us</i>
 <i>to keep things coordinated...</i>

00:23:08.467 --> 00:23:12.033 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>if you sent us progress reports</i>
 <i>as you went, but..</i>

00:23:12.067 --> 00:23:18.334 position:10% line:77% align:start
 <i>(Sasuke) Next time on Naruto</i>
 <i>Shippuden: "Sasuke's Story:</i>
 <i>Sunrise, Part 2: Coliseum."</i>

00:23:18.367 --> 00:23:20.934 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'm merely doing what I</i>
 <i>need to do.</i>

